.DT
query_wimpy
Discworld living help
query_wimpy

Name
.SI 5
query_wimpy - The wimpy value.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
int query_wimpy();
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Returns the wimpy value of the monster.  This is the value it used
for adjustment of xp and for when to run away from a fight.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
query_wimpy, adjust_xp, set_xp, query_xp
.EP
